&lt;li&gt;Own at least one functional domain area for the Safety Policy team beyond your harm portfolio. Current team needs include policy implementation systems, AI/LLM governance, or safety-by-design frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expected travel: 15%&lt;/li&gt;
