&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work hands-on with data engineering&lt;/strong&gt; — dig into pipeline architecture, instrumentation, and data modeling, not just dashboard design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prioritize ruthlessly&lt;/strong&gt; — different partner teams want different things from the data; decide what we build and in what order.&lt;/li&gt;
